### =========================================================
### Product Void Scenario
### =========================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@contentType = application/json
@brandAccessToken = REPLACE_BRAND_TENANT_TOKEN
@tenantId = REPLACE_TENANT_ID
@groupId = REPLACE_BRAND_GROUP_ID
@passportId = REPLACE_PASSPORT_ID

### 1) Void Asset
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/tenants/{{tenantId}}/groups/{{groupId}}/passports/{{passportId}}/void
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "reason": "COUNTERFEIT_DETECTED",
  "note": "Counterfeit confirmed by inspection team"
}

### 2) Verify asset state after void
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/passports/{{passportId}}/state
Authorization: Bearer {{brandAccessToken}}
